    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "CP-03-AI-Copywriter-Bonus\n\nSub-workflow that generates the article draft.\n\nSteps:\n1. Receives topic, keyword, and tone from the main pipeline.\n2. Builds the AI copywriting prompt.\n3. Sends the prompt to the OpenAI LLM chain.\n4. Parses and formats the AI response.\n5. Creates a Google Doc for the generated draft.\n6. Inserts the generated content into the Google Doc.\n7. Logs metadata such as topic, tone, document link, and creation time in Google Sheets.\n8. Returns the generated draft information back to the main pipeline.",
        "height": 288,
        "width": 608
      },
